'''麻醉药物和危险药物管理局'''（{{lang|en| '''Bureau of Narcotics and Dangerous Drugs'''}}，简称BNDD）是[[美国缉毒局|美国缉毒局]]的前身。它建立于1968年，是[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]的下属机构，包括由原属于[[美国财政部|美国财政部]]的麻醉药物管理局（Bureau of Narcotics）和原属[[美国卫生及公共服务部|卫生及公共服务部]]下属机构[[美国食品药品监督管理局|食品药品监督管理局]]的滥用毒品控制局（Bureau of Drug Abuse Control）合并而成。

1971年，该局共有1,500名职员，年预算为约4300万美元。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.druglibrary.org/schaffer/history/aof/aof11.html |title=The Narcotics Business:John Ingersoll's Version |access-date=2010-11-19 |archive-date=2020-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209062847/http://www.druglibrary.org/schaffer/History/aof/aof11.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1971年1月，[[中央情报局|中央情报局]]局长{{link-en|理查德·赫尔姆斯|Richard Helms}}批准了一项由麻醉药物和危险药物管理局局长{{link-en|约翰·英格索尔|John Ingersoll}}提议的“对BNDD的秘密招募和安保支持”计划。<ref name=GWU29>{{cite web |url= http://www.gwu.edu/~nsarchiv/NSAEBB/NSAEBB222/family_jewels_pt1_ocr.pdf |title= CIA's "Family Jewels" - Part 1 |pages= 29 |accessdate= 2008-06-16 |publisher= Central Intelligence Agency |archive-date= 2013-07-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130713081535/http://www.gwu.edu/~nsarchiv/NSAEBB/NSAEBB222/family_jewels_pt1_ocr.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/history/deahistory_01.htm |title= DEA History Book 1970 - 1975 |accessdate= 2008-06-16 |publisher= Drug Enforcement Administration |quote= John E. Ingersoll served as Director of the U.S. Bureau of Narcotics and Dangerous Drugs (BNDD) from 1968 until 1973. |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080223195621/http://www.usdoj.gov/dea/pubs/history/deahistory_01.htm |archivedate= 2008-02-23 }}</ref>英格索尔怀疑其属下存在[[警察腐败|腐败现象]]，要求中情局协助查处蛀虫。<ref name=GWU62>{{cite web |url= http://www.gwu.edu/~nsarchiv/NSAEBB/NSAEBB222/family_jewels_pt1_ocr.pdf |title= CIA's "Family Jewels" - Part 1 |pages= 62 |accessdate= 2008-06-16 |publisher= Central Intelligence Agency |archive-date= 2013-07-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130713081535/http://www.gwu.edu/~nsarchiv/NSAEBB/NSAEBB222/family_jewels_pt1_ocr.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>

1973年，该局并入新成立的美国缉毒局。

